Due to the epidemic situation, many graduates failed to experience the ritual sense of picking ears and awarding degree certificates on the spot, so they transferred the ritual sense to the online.
Data show that the 2.5-hour concert has a peak popularity of more than 35 million live broadcasts.
"Follow your heart, seize the opportunity, regardless of the consequences, sometimes there will be unexpected gains."
