Water control should start from the source.
In Yinchuan, Ningxia, the local government adopted the method of "standard raising + pollution control + strict management". All sewage in the industrial park was treated centrally, all urban sewage treatment plants were discharged according to Class A standard, and black and smelly water bodies in urban built-up areas were basically eliminated. The third batch of China's black and smelly water demonstration cities were successfully declared.
