Xinhua News Agency, Kuala Lumpur, July 25 (Reporter Lin Hao) The video conference of trade ministers of APEC members was held on the 25th. The meeting promised to work to reduce the impact of COVID-19 Epidemic on the regional economy and accelerate the realization of flexible, sustainable and inclusive regional economic recovery.
